The event would become known as The Salem Witch Trials,

00:01:37.073 --> 00:01:40.143
arguably the most famous witch trials in history.

00:01:41.223 --> 00:01:47.803
It all began after two young girls in the village, Betty Parris and her cousin Abigail Williams

00:01:48.173 --> 00:01:55.393
started experiencing horrible episodes of seizures, screaming, and pain throughout their bodies.

